tags: I lost a fic shame on me
body:
Looking for fic title

So I really thought I bookmarked the fic or it was still one of my 100+ tabs in my phone but I lost it *cries*

I am looking for this Danbeau fic where Maria would wake up early to avoid seeing Carol the whole day. So one day Carol confronts her about it and Maria is releasing all her hidden feeling about losing Carol once and such. Then they end up making out in the kitchen with Maria in control.

Does someone remember the title of that fic????

Also I wonder if anyone rememebr that fic where Carol remembers she loves Maria by talking with Monica about the Roman Empire and Carol is starting to remember her trip to Rome with Maria. Seems that fic has been deleted on AO3 *cries*

blog.description: Ask blog for everyone’s favorite a-holes. It’s a little good. It’s a little bad. It’s a bit of both.

summary: Carol, I'm curious. How exactly do you know Peter?
question: Carol, I'm curious. How exactly do you know Peter?
answer: I’m glad you asked. Back in 1980, Maria and I were living near Meredith and Peter. She couldn’t always take him to work, so I babysat Peter for her. We always had a blast together. I always called him Major Trouble. I still do; actually…I was so worried when I found out he got abducted off of Earth. I wish I could’ve been there for him sooner….all that time I thought he and Meri were both dead…

summary: #REBLOGGING THIS AGAIN BECAUSE I FORGOT TO MENTION#remember how it's a huge thing in kree culture#that you never tell ANYONE who...
body:
#REBLOGGING THIS AGAIN BECAUSE I FORGOT TO MENTION#remember how it’s a huge thing in kree culture#that you never tell ANYONE who you see when you visit the supreme intelligence??#AND SHE TOLD HIM?????#BECAUSE SHE TRUSTS HIM THAT MUCH????? (@jennathearcher​)

Yes, and even more amazing: She asks Yon-Rogg who he sees and even nags him about it.

Vers knows Yon-Rogg is the poster boy of the Kree. He’s been trying since six years to make her less emotional because that’s the Kree way of thinking/living.
She knows he’s really focused on following the rules and is pretty much exactly what the Kree aspire to be.
She knows the Kree never tell anyone who they see the Supreme Intelligence as because it’s so private to them.

Yet she asks. In fact, it’s literally her immediate reaction (”It’s personal. No Kree divulges it. Ever.” - “Who do you see?”). And she keeps guessing people when he refuses to answer. It’s obviously weird to her that he won’t tell her so she must be used to Yon-Rogg sharing everything with her, no matter how personal it is. And that’s beautiful.

(And she’s probably also used to him always giving in when she just annoys him enough which is why she keeps doing it. She rightfully never fears it will anger him because, as it’s shown in the film, it really just amuses him.)

summary:
Captain Marvel (2019) dir.

Anna Boden, Ryan Fleck. 7.4/10 About Vers trying to remember who she was but also trying to control...
caption:
Captain Marvel (2019) dir. Anna Boden, Ryan Fleck.
7.4/10

About Vers trying to remember who she was but also trying to control her powers. She’s trying to stop the war happening in outer space until she comes across where she once grew up and the secrets that led to her being here. 

I’m dead at goose on the plane. 

I like it when Brie Larson laughs. 

It was a good touch to add in the little kid so it can show women empowerment and also kid empowerment. 

I love how everything comes full circle. I wanna rewatch all of marvel. 

Memorable Quotes:
“Anger only serves the enemy.”
